2lkZ2V0TmFtZT1zcF9tdGY&amp;psc=1&amp;asin=B0C47PN5KF&amp;revisionId=&amp;format=4&amp;depth=1">several </a><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dinosaur-Coloring-Book-Awesome-Kids/dp/B0C7F75Y61/ref=sr_1_55?crid=26A0QLWD0MB5T&amp;keywords=dinosaur+coloring+book&amp;qid=1686881027&amp;sprefix=dinosaur+coloring+book%2Caps%2C1344&amp;sr=8-55&amp;asin=B0C7F75Y61&amp;revisionId=&amp;format=4&amp;depth=1">near identical</a> copies all sold under different names. Note how some have missing legs, or extra legs, or distorted nightmare arms. All are clearly AI works.</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2098e174-f924-406a-8b07-fd906856f95c_624x397.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2098e174-f924-406a-8b07-fd906856f95c_624x397.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2098e174-f924-406a-8b07-fd906856f95c_624x397.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2098e174-f924-406a-8b07-fd906856f95c_624x397.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2098e174-f924-406a-8b07-fd906856f95c_624x397.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazo